{
  "video_id": "GDc6PxpAMeY",
  "title": "Why This Watch Costs Over $450,000",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 3248.0,
      "end_time": 5570.0,
      "text": "The watch comes in two different versions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 5570.0,
      "end_time": 7650.0,
      "text": "and the difference between the two is pretty much restricted"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7650.0,
      "end_time": 9440.0,
      "text": "just to the case material."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9440.0,
      "end_time": 12780.0,
      "text": "The $460,000 version is in red gold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 12780.0,
      "end_time": 13613.0,
      "text": "and the more expensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 13613.0,
      "end_time": 15238.0,
      "text": "half million dollar version"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 15245.0,
      "end_time": 16851.0,
      "text": "is done in platinum."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20650.0,
      "end_time": 23570.0,
      "text": "Many of the most expensive watches are expensive because"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 23570.0,
      "end_time": 25170.0,
      "text": "they're set with precious stones, which,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 25170.0,
      "end_time": 27170.0,
      "text": "of course, raises the price through the roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 27170.0,
      "end_time": 29370.0,
      "text": "In the case of the Récital 22 Grand Récital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 29370.0,
      "end_time": 32720.0,
      "text": "however, the watch is as expensive as it is entirely"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 32720.0,
      "end_time": 34750.0,
      "text": "because of the amount of craftsmanship that goes into it"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 34750.0,
      "end_time": 36300.0,
      "text": "and the length of time that it takes"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 36300.0,
      "end_time": 36863.0,
      "text": "to produce the various effects"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 36863.0,
      "end_time": 39188.0,
      "text": "that make the watch what it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 40270.0,
      "end_time": 42740.0,
      "text": "BOVET watches are inherently limited in production simply"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 42740.0,
      "end_time": 44580.0,
      "text": "because of the complexity that's associated"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 44580.0,
      "end_time": 45600.0,
      "text": "with making them."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 45600.0,
      "end_time": 48460.0,
      "text": "This particular watch is a limited edition"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 48460.0,
      "end_time": 50810.0,
      "text": "of 60 pieces worldwide."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 50810.0,
      "end_time": 54800.0,
      "text": "Those are going to roll out very slowly, simply because"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 54800.0,
      "end_time": 55100.0,
      "text": "they can't be made quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 55100.0,
      "end_time": 58290.0,
      "text": "It's just inherent in the nature of the watch."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 58290.0,
      "end_time": 60470.0,
      "text": "The single decorative element that's probably"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 60470.0,
      "end_time": 63519.0,
      "text": "most strongly identified with BOVET today is the use"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 63520.0,
      "end_time": 67650.0,
      "text": "of extremely fine miniature painting, often in the form of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 67650.0,
      "end_time": 70920.0,
      "text": "what's called, cold enameling on the dials of their watches."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 70920.0,
      "end_time": 74700.0,
      "text": "And the Récital 22 Grand Récital has a"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 74700.0,
      "end_time": 78700.0,
      "text": "really, really wonderful example of this particular craft."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 78700.0,
      "end_time": 80729.0,
      "text": "The centerpiece of the watch is a hemisphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 80730.0,
      "end_time": 83920.0,
      "text": "representing the Earth as seen from above the North Pole."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 83920.0,
      "end_time": 86130.0,
      "text": "There are many, many layers of enamel that have been,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 86130.0,
      "end_time": 87890.0,
      "text": "that have been applied to the hemisphere in order"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 87890.0,
      "end_time": 90400.0,
      "text": "to achieve a wonderful kind of translucent effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 90400.0,
      "end_time": 92300.0,
      "text": "in which the clouds literally seem to float"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 92300.0,
      "end_time": 94350.0,
      "text": "above the oceans and continents."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 94350.0,
      "end_time": 98429.0,
      "text": "The paints are actually luminous and very, very luminous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 98430.0,
      "end_time": 101320.0,
      "text": "and, when you turn the lights off, you are treated to a view"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 101320.0,
      "end_time": 103000.0,
      "text": "of the continents glowing up at you"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 103000.0,
      "end_time": 105130.0,
      "text": "that's just incredibly compelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 105130.0,
      "end_time": 107770.0,
      "text": "This particular wristwatch is in a class of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 107770.0,
      "end_time": 110259.0,
      "text": "what are called, astronomical complications."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 110260.0,
      "end_time": 113580.0,
      "text": "These are timepieces that show, often, the relative position"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 113580.0,
      "end_time": 115870.0,
      "text": "of the stars to an observer standing on Earth, or,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 115870.0,
      "end_time": 117640.0,
      "text": "in this case, the relative position"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 117640.0,
      "end_time": 118910.0,
      "text": "of the sun and the moon relative"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 118910.0,
      "end_time": 120610.0,
      "text": "to an observer standing on Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 120610.0,
      "end_time": 123710.0,
      "text": "So the centerpiece is this revolving hand-painted depiction"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 123710.0,
      "end_time": 126320.0,
      "text": "of the upper hemisphere, the northern hemisphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 126320.0,
      "end_time": 127500.0,
      "text": "of the Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 127500.0,
      "end_time": 130199.0,
      "text": "Placed just below it, in the six o'clock position, is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 130199.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131750.0,
      "text": "what's called, a tourbillon."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 131750.0,
      "end_time": 134880.0,
      "text": "We can see the tourbillon rotating as we look at the watch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 134880.0,
      "end_time": 137530.0,
      "text": "and the position that it's in is identical to the position"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 137530.0,
      "end_time": 139950.0,
      "text": "that the sun would be in, relative to the Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 139950.0,
      "end_time": 142140.0,
      "text": "So it kind of stands in for, the tourbillon stands in"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 142140.0,
      "end_time": 143950.0,
      "text": "for the sun in this wristwatch."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 143950.0,
      "end_time": 146649.0,
      "text": "Rotating around the Earth is a spherical depiction"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 146650.0,
      "end_time": 150200.0,
      "text": "of the moon divided into a sunlit hemisphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 150200.0,
      "end_time": 151500.0,
      "text": "and a dark hemisphere."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 151500.0,
      "end_time": 154800.0,
      "text": "And you can read the phase of the moon from the position"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 154800.0,
      "end_time": 156750.0,
      "text": "of this little hemisphere as it rotates around the Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 156750.0,
      "end_time": 159200.0,
      "text": "The back of the watch is also loaded with information."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 159200.0,
      "end_time": 161190.0,
      "text": "It's what's called the perpetual calendar."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 161190.0,
      "end_time": 163940.0,
      "text": "Now, a perpetual calendar is a mechanical watch"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 163940.0,
      "end_time": 166540.0,
      "text": "which knows the difference between a leap year"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 166540.0,
      "end_time": 169100.0,
      "text": "and a non-leap year, and which also advances the date"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 169100.0,
      "end_time": 170530.0,
      "text": "correctly at the end of each month,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 170530.0,
      "end_time": 173540.0,
      "text": "whether it's a 30-day month or a 31-day month."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 173540.0,
      "end_time": 175970.0,
      "text": "The relative rarity of the watches and the amount"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 175970.0,
      "end_time": 178580.0,
      "text": "of handwork that goes into finishing the movement, the case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 178580.0,
      "end_time": 181230.0,
      "text": "and other aspects of the watch all adds up"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 181230.0,
      "end_time": 182730.0,
      "text": "to a tremendous, tremendous amount"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 182730.0,
      "end_time": 184500.0,
      "text": "of real old-school craftsmanship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 184500.0,
      "end_time": 185990.0,
      "text": "which simply doesn't come cheap."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 185990.0,
      "end_time": 188940.0,
      "text": "At this level of watchmaking, you're really talking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 188940.0,
      "end_time": 190570.0,
      "text": "something that's designed to appeal to someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 190570.0,
      "end_time": 193602.0,
      "text": "with extremely specific tastes and with a budget to match."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 195520.0,
      "end_time": 198962.0,
      "text": "There are 705 components in this wristwatch."
    }
  ]
}